<section>
<div class="row hero-wrap">
	<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 left" id="particles-js"></div>
	<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 right">
		<div class="circle clearfix">
			<div>
				<h1>&lt;&nbsp;HELLO WORLD&nbsp;&gt;</h1>
				<p>TECH Tie-Up is a community for developers and tech enthusiast to learn, share​ ​their ​knowledge.</p>
			</div>
